author: rgrabowski
msg: Initial check-in for supporting QueryForDataTable. I've got it returning a DataTable from a <select> statement. I've also included a fixed QueryForObject for IBATISNET-104 (CachingStatement opens/closes connection to database if there is a cache hit) and the two line fix for IBATISNET-154 (allow SelectKey to specify a resultMap instead of just a resultClass).
